---
import SectionLabel from '../ui/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<section class="px-8 py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <SectionLabel class="text-center">Why Freyja Labs</SectionLabel>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-[42px] font-medium text-ink leading-tight text-center mb-14">
      Ahead of the curve,<br/>by design.
    </h2>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <blockquote class="relative font-serif text-2xl md:text-[28px] font-normal italic text-earth leading-snug px-6 mb-5">
        <span class="absolute -top-6 -left-3 font-serif text-7xl text-sand leading-none" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
        We've been delivering CS integration, computational modeling, and AI literacy workshops for years before they became policy mandates. Our clients get access to the thinking that will matter next &mdash; not the thinking that mattered last year.
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-sm text-faded">&mdash; Mike &amp; Andrea, Co-Founders</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
